  "displayTitle": "<span class=\"mw-page-title-main\">Portable Grinding Mill</span>",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output\"><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n\n<p><i>Exclusive to:</i> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve_Together\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together\"><img alt=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Don%27t_Starve_Together_icon.png/32px-Don%27t_Starve_Together_icon.png?3bc208\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\"></a><br>\n</p>\n\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n\n<p>The <b>Portable Grinding Mill</b> is a craftable <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Item\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Item\">Item</a> exclusive to <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve_Together\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together\">Don&#x27;t Starve Together</a></i>. It can only be crafted and used by <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Warly\" title=\"Warly\">Warly</a>, requiring 2 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Gold_Nugget\" title=\"Gold Nugget\">Gold Nuggets</a>, 2 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Electrical_Doodad\" title=\"Electrical Doodad\">Electrical Doodads</a>, and 4 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Twigs\" title=\"Twigs\">Twigs</a>. Like the <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Portable_Crock_Pot\" title=\"Portable Crock Pot\">Portable Crock Pot</a>, it can be held in a player&#x27;s inventory and can be placed as a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Structure\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Structure\">Structure</a>. When it is placed, it acts as a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crafting\" title=\"Crafting\">Crafting</a> station and grants access to the <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Seasonings_Filter\" title=\"Seasonings Filter\">Seasonings Filter</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2 id=\"mw-toc-heading\">Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Portable_Grinding_Mill#Crafting_Recipes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Crafting Recipes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Portable_Grinding_Mill#Skins\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Skins</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Portable_Grinding_Mill#Assets\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Assets</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Portable_Grinding_Mill#Gallery\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Gallery</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Crafting_Recipes\">Crafting Recipes</span></h2>\n<div><ul class=\"gallery mw-gallery-traditional\">\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Garlic_Powder\" title=\"Garlic Powder\"><img alt=\"Garlic Powder\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Garlic_Powder.png?41cf8c\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Garlic_Powder\" title=\"Garlic Powder\">Garlic Powder</a></div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Honey_Crystals\" title=\"Honey Crystals\"><img alt=\"Honey Crystals\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Honey_Crystals.png?da1b5f\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Honey_Crystals\" title=\"Honey Crystals\">Honey Crystals</a></div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Chili_Flakes\" title=\"Chili Flakes\"><img alt=\"Chili Flakes\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Chili_Flakes.png?35671b\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Chili_Flakes\" title=\"Chili Flakes\">Chili Flakes</a></div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Seasoning_Salt\" title=\"Seasoning Salt\"><img alt=\"Seasoning Salt\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Seasoning_Salt.png?8d2206\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Seasoning_Salt\" title=\"Seasoning Salt\">Seasoning Salt</a></div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n</ul></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Skins\"><img alt=\"Voidbag Icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Voidbag_Icon.png/32px-Voidbag_Icon.png?3b640b\" width=\"32\" height=\"33\"> Skins</span></h2>\n<p><span class=\"box headnote\"><i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Glommer%27s_Flower.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Glommer&#x27;s Flower.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Glommer%27s_Flower.png/25px-Glommer%27s_Flower.png?22167d\" width=\"25\" height=\"25\"></a> Main article:</i> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Belongings#Portables_Structures\" title=\"Belongings\">Belongings</a></span><br>\n</p>\n<div>\n<div class=\"skin-info\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Stoneware_Grinding_Mill_Icon.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Stoneware Grinding Mill Icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Stoneware_Grinding_Mill_Icon.png/88px-Stoneware_Grinding_Mill_Icon.png?5be659\" width=\"88\" height=\"120\"></a></div><div><span class=\"skin-rarity-distinguished\"><b>Woven - Distinguished</b></span></div><div class=\"skin-name\"><b>Stoneware Crock Pot</b></div><div class=\"skin-description\"><i>The line between surviving and thriving lies in the richness of the flavors you savor.</i></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"skin-info\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Silver_Grinding_Mill_Icon.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Silver Grinding Mill Icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Silver_Grinding_Mill_Icon.png/95px-Silver_Grinding_Mill_Icon.png?7fb6da\" width=\"95\" height=\"120\"></a></div><div><span class=\"skin-rarity-distinguished\"><b>Woven - Distinguished</b></span></div><div class=\"skin-name\"><b>Silver Crock Pot</b></div><div class=\"skin-description\"><i>Haute cuisine, on the go!</i></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"skin-info\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Cast_Iron_Grinding_Mill_Icon.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Cast Iron Grinding Mill Icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Cast_Iron_Grinding_Mill_Icon.png/93px-Cast_Iron_Grinding_Mill_Icon.png?55b413\" width=\"93\" height=\"120\"></a></div><div><span class=\"skin-rarity-distinguished\"><b>Woven - Distinguished</b></span></div><div class=\"skin-name\"><b>Cast Iron Crock Pot</b></div><div class=\"skin-description\"><i>Maman Angeline always favored cast iron cookware.</i></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"skin-info\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Porcelain_Grinding_Mill_Icon.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Porcelain Grinding Mill Icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Porcelain_Grinding_Mill_Icon.png/97px-Porcelain_Grinding_Mill_Icon.png?f30ceb\" width=\"97\" height=\"120\"></a></div><div><span class=\"skin-rarity-distinguished\"><b>Woven - Distinguished</b></span></div><div class=\"skin-name\"><b>Porcelain Crock Pot</b></div><div class=\"skin-description\"><i>The key ingredient is charm.</i></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Assets\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Research_Notes\" title=\"Research Notes\"><img alt=\"Research Notes.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Research_Notes.png/32px-Research_Notes.png?ef2da4\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Assets</span></h2>\n<div class