  "plainText": "Portable Grinding Mill\nObject Info\nPerk\nPortable.\nGrants access to the Seasonings Filter.\nCan be Burned\nSource\nCan be Hammered\nCan be dismantled to .\nResources\n×1\nMiscellaneous\n\"portableblender\"\nExclusive to:\nPortable Grinding Mill\n\"Grind ingredients into powdered spices.\"\nObject Info\nCan be Burned\nDoes not stack\nCrafting\n×2 ×2 ×4 ( only)\nFilters\nTier\nAlways available\nMiscellaneous\n\"portableblender_item\"\n“It mixes all the food.”\n–Wilson\n“Shakes things up a bit.”\n–Willow\n“Wolfgang could smash food like that if he wanted.”\n–Wolfgang\n“Inflicts chaos and turmoil on food.”\n–Wendy\n“WE HAVE SO MUCH IN COMMON”\n–WX-78\n“Quite a lively cooking instrument.”\n–Wickerbottom\n“Chops up food pretty good.”\n–Woodie\n“Does it have to make such a horrible racket?”\n–Maxwell\n“It döes battle with fööd.”\n–Wigfrid\n“Shake-a, shake-a, shake-a!”\n–Webber\n“It has greatly improved my culinary adventures.”\n–Warly\n“Chops belly stuff”\n–Wormwood\n“I like the way that machine dances.”\n–Winona\n“All that chopping and no souls.”\n–Wortox\n“Shaky shaky!”\n–Wurt\n“It mixes all the food together.”\n–Walter\n“It does a lively little jig.”\n–Wanda\nThe Portable Grinding Mill is a craftable Item exclusive to Don't Starve Together. It can only be crafted and used by Warly, requiring 2 Gold Nuggets, 2 Electrical Doodads, and 4 Twigs. Like the Portable Crock Pot, it can be held in a player's inventory and can be placed as a Structure. When it is placed, it acts as a Crafting station and grants access to the Seasonings Filter.\nContents\n1 Crafting Recipes\n2 Skins\n3 Assets\n4 Gallery\nCrafting Recipes[edit | edit source]\nGarlic Powder\nHoney Crystals\nChili Flakes\nSeasoning Salt\nSkins[edit | edit source]\nMain article: Belongings\nWoven - Distinguished\nStoneware Crock Pot\nThe line between surviving and thriving lies in the richness of the flavors you savor.\nWoven - Distinguished\nSilver Crock Pot\nHaute cuisine, on the go!\nWoven - Distinguished\nCast Iron Crock Pot\nMaman Angeline always favored cast iron cookware.\nWoven - Distinguished\nPorcelain Crock Pot\nThe key ingredient is charm.\nAssets[edit | edit source]\nPortable Grinding MillStoneware Grinding MillSilver Grinding MillPorcelain Grinding MillCast Iron Grinding Mill\nDropped\nIdle\nProximity\nUse\nplace\nhit\ncollapse\nburnt collapse\nburnt (unused)\nDropped\nIdle\nProximity\nUse\nplace\nhit\ncollapse\nburnt collapse\nburnt (unused)\nDropped\nIdle\nProximity\nUse\nplace\nhit\ncollapse\nburnt collapse\nburnt (unused)\nDropped\nIdle\nProximity\nUse\nplace\nhit\ncollapse\nburnt collapse\nburnt (unused)\nDropped\nIdle\nProximity\nUse\nplace\nhit\ncollapse\nburnt collapse\nburnt (unused)\nGallery[edit | edit source]\nEarlier concepts for Warly's cookware from Rhymes With Play #248.\nCraftable ItemsStructures\nView or edit this template\nDon't Starve Together Craftable Items\nRegular Filters\nSurvivor Items\nWilson\nWillow\nWolfgang\nWendy\nWX-78\nWickerbottom\nWoodie\nWes\nMaxwell\nWigfrid\nWebber\nWarly\nWortox\nWormwood\nWinona\nWurt\nWalter\nWanda\nTools\nLight Sources\nPrototypers & Stations\nRefined Materials\nWeapons\nArmor\nClothing\nHealing\nMagic\nDecorations\nStructures\nStorage Solutions\nCooking\nFood & Gardening\nFishing\nSeafaring\nBeefalo Riding\nWinter Items\nSummer Items\nRain Gear\nCrafting Station Filters\nSpecial Event\nAncient Pseudoscience\nCarpentry\nCartography\nCritters\nCelestial\nBrightsmithy\nShadowcraft\nFabrication\nBottle Exchange\nCombrining Filter\nTea Brewing Filter\nSculptures\nSeasonings\nTrading\nTrading Hutch\nOfferings\nCawnival Creation\nTrinket Trove\nMad Science\nWinter's Feast Cooking\nSanctum Smithy Filter\nCustom Course Shack Filter\nDSTDSRoGSWHam\nView or edit this template\nDon't Starve Together Structures\nAttention: The following categories are only for the players look up the page based on their first impression, they have nothing to do with the actual categories/DLC/function/tags of these Thi