  "wikitext": "{{Object Infobox\n|image=Portable_Grinding_Mill_Build.png\n|canBeBurned = 1\n|picked = Can be dismantled to {{pic24|Portable Grinding_ Mill}}.\n|resources = {{pic24|Portable Grinding_ Mill}}&times;1\n|tool = Can be [[Tools#Hammering Tools|Hammered]] {{pic|32|Hammer}}\n|perk = Portable.<br>Grants access to the [[Seasonings Filter]].\n|spawnCode = \"portableblender\"}}\n{{Exclusivity|Don't Starve Together}}\n{{Object Infobox\n|icon = Portable Grinding Mill.png\n|image = Portable Grinding Mill Dropped.png\n|name = Portable Grinding Mill\n|description = Grind ingredients into powdered spices.\n|ingredient1 = Gold Nugget\n|multiplier1 = 2\n|ingredient2 = Electrical Doodad\n|multiplier2 = 2\n|ingredient3 = Twigs\n|multiplier3 = 4 ({{pic24|Warly Portrait}} only)\n|canBeBurned = 1\n|filter = {{Pic32|Cooking Filter}} {{Pic32|Warly Filter}}\n|tier = 0\n|place = {{pic|32|Portable Grinding Mill Build|Portable Grinding Mill}}\n|stack = Does not stack\n|spawnCode = \"portableblender_item\"}}\n{{Quotes\n|wilson=It mixes all the food.\n|willow=Shakes things up a bit.\n|wolfgang=Wolfgang could smash food like that if he wanted.\n|wendy=Inflicts chaos and turmoil on food.\n|wx78=WE HAVE SO MUCH IN COMMON\n|wickerbottom=Quite a lively cooking instrument.\n|woodie=Chops up food pretty good.\n|maxwell=Does it have to make such a horrible racket?\n|wigfrid=It döes battle with fööd.\n|webber=Shake-a, shake-a, shake-a!\n|winona=I like the way that machine dances.\n|warly=It has greatly improved my culinary adventures.\n|wortox=All that chopping and no souls.\n|wormwood=Chops belly stuff\n|wurt = Shaky shaky!\n|walter = It mixes all the food together.\n|wanda = It does a lively little jig.\n|choose=warly}}\nThe '''Portable Grinding Mill''' is a craftable [[Item]] exclusive to ''[[Don't Starve Together]]''. It can only be crafted and used by [[Warly]], requiring 2 [[Gold Nugget]]s, 2 [[Electrical Doodad]]s, and 4 [[Twigs]]. Like the [[Portable Crock Pot]], it can be held in a player's inventory and can be placed as a [[Structure]]. When it is placed, it acts as a [[Crafting]] station and grants access to the [[Seasonings Filter]].\n\n== Crafting Recipes ==\n{{#lst:Seasonings Filter|Craftable Items}}\n\n== [[File:Skins Icon.png|32px|link=]] Skins ==\n<noinclude>{{Main|Belongings#Portables Structures|Belongings}}</noinclude>\n<div style=\"display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px; justify-content: center;\">\n{{SkinInfo\n|image = Stoneware Grinding Mill Icon.png\n|rarity = Woven - Distinguished\n|name = Stoneware Crock Pot\n|description = The line between surviving and thriving lies in the richness of the flavors you savor.\n}}\n{{SkinInfo\n|image = Silver Grinding Mill Icon.png\n|rarity = Woven - Distinguished\n|name = Silver Crock Pot\n|description = Haute cuisine, on the go!\n}}\n{{SkinInfo\n|image = Cast Iron Grinding Mill Icon.png\n|rarity = Woven - Distinguished\n|name = Cast Iron Crock Pot\n|description = Maman Angeline always favored cast iron cookware.\n}}\n{{SkinInfo\n|image = Porcelain Grinding Mill Icon.png\n|rarity = Woven - Distinguished\n|name = Porcelain Crock Pot\n|description = The key ingredient is charm.\n}}\n</div>\n\n== {{Pic32|Research Notes}} Assets ==\n<tabber>\nPortable Grinding Mill=\n<gallery>\nPortable Grinding Mill.png|Dropped\nPortable_Grinding_Mill_Build.png|Idle\nPortable Grinding Mill Proximity.gif|Proximity\nPortable Grinding Mill Use.gif|Use\nPortable Grinding Mill Place.gif|place\nPortable Grinding Mill Hit.gif|hit\nPortable Grinding Mill Collapse.gif|collapse\nPortable Grinding Mill Burnt Collapse.gif|burnt collapse\nPortable Grinding Mill_Burnt.png|burnt (unused)\n</gallery>\n|-|\nStoneware Grinding Mill=\n<gallery>\nStoneware Grinding Mill Dropped.png|Dropped\nStoneware Grinding Mill Build.png|Idle\nStoneware Grinding Mill Proximity.gif|Proximity\nStoneware Grinding Mill Use.gif|Use\nStoneware Grinding Mill Place.gif|place\nStoneware Grinding Mill Hit.gif|hit\nStoneware Grinding Mill Collapse.gif|collapse\nStoneware Grinding Mill Burnt Collapse.gif|burnt collapse\nStoneware Grinding Mill_Burnt.png|burnt (unused)\n</gallery>\n|-|\nSilver Grinding Mill=\n<gallery>\nSilver Grinding Mill Dropped.png|Dropped\nSilver Grinding Mill Build.png|Idle\nSilver Grinding Mill Proximity.gif|Proximity\nSilver Grinding Mill Use.gif|Use\nSilver Grinding Mill Place.gif|place\nSilver Grinding Mill Hit.gif|hit\nSilver Grinding Mill Collapse.gif|collapse\nSilver Grinding Mill Burnt Collapse.gif|burnt collapse\nSilver Grinding Mill_Burnt.png|burnt (unused)\n</gallery>\n|-|\nPorcelain Grinding Mill=\n<gallery>\nPorcelain Grinding Mill Dropped.png|Dropped\nPorcelain Grinding Mill Build.png|Idle\nPorcelain Grinding Mill Proximity.gif|Proximity\nPorcelain Grinding Mill Use.gif|Use\nPorcelain Grinding Mill Place.gif|place\nPorcelain Grinding Mill Hit.gif|hit\nPorcelain Grinding Mill Collapse.gif|collapse\nPorcelain Grinding Mill Burnt Collapse.gif|burnt collapse\nPorcelain Grinding Mill_Burnt.png|burnt (unused)\n</gallery>\n|-|\nCast Iron Grinding Mill=\n<gallery>\nCast Iron Grinding Mill Dropped.png|Dropped\nCast Iron Grinding Mill Build.png|Idle\nCast Iron Grinding Mill Proximity.gif|Proximity\nCast Iron Grinding Mill Use.gif|Use\nCast Iron Grinding Mill Place.gif|place\nCast Iron Grinding Mill Hit.gif|hit\nCast Iron Grinding Mill Collapse.gif|collapse\nCast Iron Grinding Mill Burnt Collapse.gif|burnt collapse\nCast Iron Grinding Mill_Burnt.png|burnt (unused)\n</gallery>\n</tabber>\n=={{Pic32|Blueprint}} Gallery==\n<gallery captionalign=\"center\" hideaddbutton=\"true\">\nRWP 248 Warly's Cookware.png|Earlier concepts for Warly's cookware from ''Rhymes With Play'' #248.\n</gallery>\n{{Clear}}\n<tabber>\nCraftable Items=\n{{Craftable Items and Structures on DST}}\n|-|\nStructures=\n{{Structures}}\n</tabber>\n[[ru:Переносная мельница]] [[pt:Moedor Portátil (Portable Grinding Mill)]]\n[[zh:便携研磨器]]\n[[Category:Survivor Items Filter]]\n[[Category:Cooking Filter]]\n[[Category:Crafting Stations]]